# Library Search & URL Unit – Protected

**Do NOT modify** the search and URL paste/drop functionality unless the user explicitly asks for changes in that area.

## Protected scope

- `components/library-input-area.tsx` – the combined search + URL paste/drop unit
- Search box (YouTube, library search, voice search)
- URL input, paste, and drag-and-drop
- "Paste or Drop URL" zone and its styling

## When to modify

Only touch this code when the user **specifically** requests changes to:
- The search box
- The URL paste/drop area
- Related behavior or styling

## When NOT to modify

- General feature requests
- Bug fixes in other parts of the app
- Refactoring or "improvements" that might affect this unit
